That‚Äôs also why I chose "Smells Like Teen Spirit" as the soundtrack‚Äîit just felt right.  Huge thanks to Adenex, Lauransky, and Kit for their incredible tools that make it possible for creators to bring CS2 moments to life in Unreal Engine.
